# faActionManager (`src/scripts/actionManager/`)

**Renderer-side action manager** = **single funnel** for user-meaningful UI actions: dialog opens, settings saves, window controls, language switch, dev tools, startup notifications, etc. Routes **all** failures through one console row + one toast ‚Äî no ad-hoc **`Notify.create`** across stores/call sites.

## Mental model

- **Action ids**: **`types/I_faActionManagerDomain.ts`** (**`FA_ACTION_IDS`**, **`T_faActionId`**, **`I_faActionPayloadMap`**). Payload map ties each id to handler input (`void` = no payload).
- **Definitions**: **`src/scripts/actionManager/faActionDefinitions.ts`** (**`FA_ACTION_DEFINITIONS`**) ‚Äî each id ‚Üí **`kind`** (**`async`** / **`sync`**), optional **`dedup`**, **`handler`** ref. **Handlers**: **`faActionDefinitionHandlers.ts`** so definitions table stays shallow id list.
- **Run APIs** (**`faActionManagerRun.ts`**):
  - **`runFaAction(id, payload)`** ‚Äî fire-and-forget; call site never sees errors.
  - **`runFaActionAwait(id, payload): Promise<boolean>`** ‚Äî same dispatch; **`true`** success, **`false`** failure (toast + console still emitted).
- **Sync queue** (**`faActionManagerSyncQueue.ts`**): **FIFO**, one-at-a-time, **30 s** timeout (**`FA_ACTION_SYNC_TIMEOUT_MS`**), **soft cap 32** (**`FA_ACTION_SYNC_QUEUE_MAX`**), opt-in **`dedup`** drops duplicates while pending/running, **`awaitSyncQueueDrain()`** waits empty.
- **Async path**: runs immediately; tracks entry in **`S_FaActionManager.inFlightAsyncActions`** until resolve/reject.
- **Error surface** (**`faActionManagerErrorReporting_manager.ts`**, factory **`functions/createFaActionManagerErrorReporting.ts`**, captions **`faActionManagerErrorReportingNormalize.ts`**): **`reportFaActionFailure`** ‚Üí exactly **one** **`console.error`** + **one** **`Notify.create`** per failure (**`type: 'negative'`** default; **`FaProjectOpenFailedError`** may **`type: 'warning'`** for softer UX; console + history stay failure-shaped); hard project-open failures use **`.faproject`** path as toast caption; also **`S_FaActionManager.lastFailure`**.
- **History** (**`faActionManagerHistory.ts`**): session-only ring buffer (cap **`FA_ACTION_HISTORY_MAX = 500`** in **`S_FaActionManager`**); **`DialogActionMonitor`** via **`snapshotActionHistory()`** (deep-cloned, sorted desc by **`enqueuedAt`**).
- **Store bridge** (**`faActionManagerStoreBridge.ts`**): **`resolveFaActionManagerStore()`** ‚Üí **`null`** without Pinia ‚Äî safe tests + early boot.

## Single-toast rule

Action manager **only** place for **error** toasts on registered actions. Store handlers (e.g. **`S_FaKeybinds.updateKeybinds`**, **`S_FaUserSettings.updateSettings`**) **must throw** on failure (or **`false`** + console) ‚Äî **no** own negative **`Notify.create`** for save errors. Success toasts may stay in stores when user-relevant (e.g. "Settings saved").

## Adding a new action (checklist)

1. **`types/I_faActionManagerDomain.ts`** ‚Äî append id to **`FA_ACTION_IDS`**, payload to **`I_faActionPayloadMap`** (`void` if none).
2. **`faActionDefinitionHandlers.ts`** ‚Äî **`export async function handle‚Ä¶`** (or sync **`export function`**). **`faActionDefinitions.ts`** ‚Äî append **`FA_ACTION_DEFINITIONS`** row: **`kind`** (**`sync`** ordered window controls; **`async`** dialog opens/fire-and-forget). **`dedup: true`** when rapid double-trigger should collapse.
3. **Call sites** ‚Äî **`runFaAction`** / **`runFaActionAwait`** instead of direct UI/store/bridge calls.
4. **Tests** ‚Äî **`src/scripts/actionManager/_tests/`**, Vitest for migrated call sites, **`src/scripts/keybinds/_tests/`** when **`FA_KEYBIND_COMMAND_TO_ACTION_ID`** changes. **Connected UI**: **`DialogActionMonitor/_tests/`** (Vitest + Playwright), **`e2e-tests/checkActionMonitor.playwright.spec.ts`**, E2E opening monitor (e.g. **`checkKeybinds.playwright.spec.ts`**) when table columns, copy, **`L_DialogActionMonitor`**, history shape changes ‚Äî **grep** **`DialogActionMonitor`**, **`dialogActionMonitor`**, action id.
5. **Keybind routing (optional)** ‚Äî global shortcut ‚Üí **`FA_KEYBIND_COMMAND_TO_ACTION_ID`** in **`faKeybindRunCommand.ts`** + **`I_faKeybindCommandDefinition`** ([fantasia-keybinds](../skills/fantasia-keybinds/SKILL.md)).
6. **Action monitor** ‚Äî no extra wiring; new id appears in **`DialogActionMonitor`** once executed.

## Authoring constraints

- **Module/function size** ‚Äî **`src/scripts/actionManager/`** within global **‚â§250 lines/module**, **‚â§100 lines/function** ([code-size-decomposition.mdc](code-size-decomposition.mdc)). Split registry vs run vs sync queue vs error vs history vs store bridge.
- **No direct `Notify.create` for action failures** ‚Äî **`reportFaActionFailure`** or manager automatic path. Sync queue overflow drops = dedicated toast + synthetic **`failed`** history row.
- **Handler errors** ‚Äî throw/reject OK; manager catches, **`normalizeFaActionError`**, **`reportFaActionFailure`**.
- **Payload preview** ‚Äî always **`buildFaActionPayloadPreview`** for log/history. Cycles/unserializable ‚Üí **`[unserializable]`**; long previews truncated for monitor table.
- **Pinia tolerance** ‚Äî never assume store mounted; **`resolveFaActionManagerStore()`** **`null`** early boot/tests without Pinia; helpers short-circuit cleanly.
- **Handler deps typing** ‚Äî **`satisfies I_createFaActionDefinitionHandlers‚Ä¶Deps`** on deps objects; use **`DeepReadonly<Ref<‚Ä¶>>`** in dep interfaces when stores expose **`readonly()`** refs.

## Tests

**Cross-surface sweep:** definitions + history power **`DialogActionMonitor`**. Monitor behavior, **`i18n/*/dialogs/L_DialogActionMonitor.ts`**, row JSON changes ‚Üí **`DialogActionMonitor`** Vitest + Playwright, **`checkActionMonitor.playwright.spec.ts`**, related E2E ([fantasia-testing](../skills/fantasia-testing/SKILL.md) **Connected tests for any feature change**).

Vitest **`src/scripts/actionManager/_tests/`**:

- **`faActionDefinitions.vitest.test.ts`** ‚Äî every **`FA_ACTION_IDS`** has definition; no duplicate ids; valid **`kind`**.
- **`faActionManagerErrorReporting.vitest.test.ts`** ‚Äî preview, normalization, single console + toast, store recording.
- **`faActionManagerHistory.vitest.test.ts`** ‚Äî queued/running/success/failed, overflow drops, snapshot ordering + deep clone.
- **`faActionManagerSyncQueue.vitest.test.ts`** ‚Äî FIFO, dedup, **`FA_ACTION_SYNC_QUEUE_MAX`** overflow, handler-throw, unknown id.
- **`faActionManagerRun.vitest.test.ts`** ‚Äî async/sync dispatch, **`runFaActionAwait`** success/failure, unknown id.
- **`faActionManagerStoreBridge.vitest.test.ts`** ‚Äî null without Pinia, resolved with active Pinia.

